workflow: JorkiLLMSession
intent: simulate an LLM querying a JORKI-indexed file — read meta, read summary, search, retrieve only needed chunk, verify merkle root
step 1: read meta → meta
step 2: read summary → summary
step 3: search index → search_hits
step 4: retrieve chunk 0 → chunk_bytes
step 5: verify hash integrity → integrity
step 6: issue receipt → session_receipt
artifact: session_receipt
receipt: SHA256 chained — LLM session proof
value: LLM queried file through compact index without downloading full file
